Package com.spotify.github.v3.prs

Interface PullRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CloseTracking, PullRequestItem, UpdateTracking
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ImmutablePullRequest
    @Immutable
public interface PullRequest
extends PullRequestItem
    Pull request resource represents data returned by a single PR get operation. It contains all the fields from PullRequestItem entity.
